=head1 DESCRIPTION

The recorder configuration consists of the local C<MediaSourceConfig>
details that are used as credentials to accesss the local media files
streamed on the camera.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> MediaSourceConfig => L<Paws::KinesisVideo::MediaSourceConfig>

The configuration details that consist of the credentials required
(C<MediaUriSecretArn> and C<MediaUriType>) to access the media files
streamed to the camera.


=head2 ScheduleConfig => L<Paws::KinesisVideo::ScheduleConfig>

The configuration that consists of the C<ScheduleExpression> and the
C<DurationInMinutes> details that specify the scheduling to record from
a camera, or local media file, onto the Edge Agent. If the
C<ScheduleExpression> attribute is not provided, then the Edge Agent
will always be set to recording mode.



